		<div class="post" id="post-35">
			<h2><a href="http://kaos.to/blog/archives/2005/07/15/armor-your-palace-securing-your-home-and-network/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Armor Your Palace">Armor Your Palace</a></h2>
				<p class="comment_edit">   <span class="comment_link"> </span></p>
				<div class="time_link">July 15th, 2005 by dr.kaos </div>	
			<div class="entry">
					<p><em>A guide to securing your home and home network with inexpensive hardware, open source software and about 8 hours of dedicated time. This is a living document, updated on a regular basis to reflect additional best practice methodologies, tips and tricks as they become available.<br />
</em><br />
<script type="text/javascript"><!--
google_ad_client = "pub-6778109320240865";
google_ad_width = 336;
google_ad_height = 280;
google_ad_format = "336x280_as";
