			<p>I would really like to see a full write-up / howto on building and configuring OSSIM for Gentoo.  When you get some extra time, which I know you&#8217;ll have plenty of after Beth goes to New York, you should write down everything you had to do to get OSSIM fully functional on Gentoo.</p>
