						<br />

			<small class="commentmetadata"><a href="#comment-27" title="">August 10th, 2005 at 11:12 am</a> </small>

			<p>[...]  security, using ip cammeras to monitor physical access and OSSIM to monitor your network. kaos.theory: fractal blog » Blog Archive » Armor Yo [...]</p>

		</li>

	
	
		<li id="comment-93">
